# Sync Engine Rules

- Sync outbox must be per user/device/session.
- Use idempotency key: `{serverUserId}:{deviceId}:{operationId}`.
- Retry must not create duplicate server records.
- Pull updates Android rows by uuid, never by local id.
- Attachment upload uses a separate queue.
- Server validates user, device, project assignment, permission, and closing period.
- Server rejected data must remain visible locally with reason.
